name: PickMe
0:
”Alexa, open pick me”
”Alexa, ask pick me to choose between chinese american or mexican”
”pick chinese american or mexican”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pick me
des: You find the ideas, we pick them for you! Having trouble making a decision? Pick Me does it for you! Ask what you are deciding between, and Pick Me will pick an option! No more debating or wasting time making a decision.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
